<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <title>Welcome to Fifty Firsts Wellness Administration</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=League+Spartan:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Quicksand', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #374151;
        background-color: #f3f4f6;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #f3f4f6;
        padding: 40px 20px;
      }

      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 0;
      }

      .email-header {
        padding: 32px 40px 24px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .logo-container {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .logo-img {
        height: 60px;
        width: auto;
      }

      .social-icons {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .social-icon {
        display: inline-block;
        width: 24px;
        height: 24px;
        color: #6b7280;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .social-icon svg {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
      }

      .email-content {
        padding: 36px 40px;
      }

      .content-title {
        font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #111827;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }

      .greeting {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #374151;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }

      .content-text {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #4b5563;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .admin-badge {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #111827;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 4px 12px;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      .feature-list {
        margin: 20px 0;
      }

      .feature-item {
        padding: 12px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }

      .feature-item:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      .feature-text {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #374151;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .security-notice {
        background-color: #f9fafb;
        border-left: 3px solid #f59e0b;
        padding: 12px;
        margin: 16px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #92400e;
      }

      .btn-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 14px 32px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 0;
        background-color: #00969b;
        color: #ffffff;
        transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
      }

      .btn:hover {
        background-color: #007a7e;
      }

      .email-footer {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        padding: 24px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .footer-text {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #6b7280;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .footer-link {
        color: #00969b;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .footer-link:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .footer-copyright {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #9ca3af;
        margin-top: 24px;
        padding-top: 24px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }

      @media only screen and (max-width: 640px) {
        .email-wrapper {
          padding: 20px 10px;
        }

        .email-header {
          padding: 24px 20px 20px;
        }

        .logo-img {
          height: 60px;
        }

        .social-icons {
          gap: 8px;
        }

        .social-icon {
          width: 18px;
          height: 18px;
        }

        .email-content {
          padding: 32px 20px;
        }

        .content-title {
          font-size: 24px;
        }

        .btn {
          display: block;
          width: 100%;
          padding: 16px;
        }

        .email-footer {
          padding: 24px 20px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">

          <h1 class="content-title">Welcome to the Leadership Team</h1>

          <p class="greeting">Hi <%= firstName || 'there' %>,</p>

          <p class="content-text">
            Congratulations on joining the Fifty Firsts Wellness administration team! You're now part of a mission to empower individuals through midlife transitions and wellness transformation.
          </p>

          <div class="feature-list">
            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-text">
                <strong>Team Management:</strong> Lead and support our community of wellness professionals
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-text">
                <strong>Platform Oversight:</strong> Monitor and optimize the user experience and content quality
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-text">
                <strong>Security & Compliance:</strong> Ensure platform safety and maintain community standards
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-text">
                <strong>Growth Strategy:</strong> Contribute to expanding our impact and reaching more individuals
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="security-notice">
            <strong>Security Reminder:</strong> As an administrator, you have access to sensitive information. Please ensure you follow all security protocols and maintain the highest standards of confidentiality.
          </div>

          <div class="btn-container">
            <a href="<%= frontendUrl %>/admin/dashboard" class="btn">Access Admin Dashboard</a>
          </div>

          <p class="content-text" style="margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 0;">
            Thanks,<br>
            Fifty Firsts Wellness Team
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="email-footer">
          <div class="footer-text">
            Questions or FAQ? Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@fiftyfirstswellness.co.uk" class="footer-link">info@fiftyfirstswellness.co.uk</a>
          </div>

          <div class="footer-copyright">
            Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Fifty Firsts Wellness. All rights reserved.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
